{"tid":1617140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「Green object」變成「休班 object」時，便成為我們的擦經驗的對象","createTime":"2019-10-03T16:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T06:52:54.000Z","uid":178092,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"47c1539c4c3a57fc9d3d46c99c92beff2faf9c60","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9c1d36bdc1ee665b15f4c1e6ced00774c34ea7e9","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"47c1539c4c3a57fc9d3d46c99c92beff2faf9c60","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"當謀殺市民被&quot;正當&quot;化 市民做乜都已經唔需要太多解釋 謀殺學生一事 已經在世界各地被傳播 就算有咩行動都屬自然反應<br />\n<br />\nGreen Object同佢嘅紅色液體 將會被其所掀起嘅黑色浪潮淹沒"},{"pid":"2391fb2b3a1bd4d7ae0f0b42b18af7dd25750af1","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5a3b45abad81f10f7941948f69a5115f4e2b9d2","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:11:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99f978b31d8aa6467b939015df814de0732373a8","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢見到李小龍 竟然記得個夢講咩<br />\n<br />\n十月一日 遍地開花 證明香港兒女不是病夫 有部分人已經豁左出去 願承擔受傷被捕嘅風險<br />\n<br />\n小龍佢好感動 係呢個武力咁懸殊嘅情況下 大家都向前衝 呢一個moment 香港人係一條心<br />\n<br />\n但係 佢同時亦都極度心痛 大量手足被捕 當中受到不同程度嘅傷害<br />\n<br />\n小龍佢係咁諗嘅：我地嘅優勢係人多 但係手足少一個得一個&nbsp;每一個手足都好重要！！<br />\n警隊放鬆武力守則 擺明居馬講你知 你同佢地對抗 佢就會乘機虐殺你&nbsp;佢知道佢地只能贏 就算係幾唔合法嘅事 都會被默許/支持 或被講成合法<br />\n所以&nbsp;為左減低各位手足被明槍射殺嘅風險 小龍希望有啲野唔好係大街做&nbsp;大家開始揾下你身邊嘅好鄰居 尤其係嗰啲守護香港嘅&quot;好警察&quot; Green Object 俾啲教訓佢地&nbsp;記住記住fact check變得更加重要<br />\n<br />\n人類不斷製造污水 必終承受污水之禍<br />\n<br />\nbe water<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油 萬事小心"},{"pid":"e26469273e255f6efa8c27a6d94b26d065625a01","tid":1617140,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbd31437cf05a97d549eba65bdb5e4b5361005d5","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:12:45.000Z","msg":"警隊放寬武力指引給香港人嘅啟示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616810</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1782221929888023ccc3a4920e13fe06a9f301e1","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3006856f8c433489c28c26893744bac8b62a64f2","tid":1617140,"uid":262146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正式要出麻包袋</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d5274edda8b14592724312fba7a779b741d4c3f0","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3006856f8c433489c28c26893744bac8b62a64f2","tid":1617140,"uid":262146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正式要出麻包袋</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"一定要 或者更簡單直接"},{"pid":"d347fa014fc5688173a9cfdfb6a04d7eef10b9c8","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"唔想睇到手足俾人亂槍射殺"},{"pid":"22f1010ac1523fd94aec89611792de478aa13be5","tid":1617140,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18cf406bb76f86752058b79d3c1283a1252caa74","tid":1617140,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo